<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #f5f5f7;
    --card: #ffffff;
    --text: #1d1d1f;
    --text-secondary: #6e6e73;
    --blue: #0071e3;
    --blue-light: #e8f2fd;
    --green: #34c759;
    --orange: #ff9f0a;
    --red: #ff3b30;
    --purple: #af52de;
    --teal: #5ac8fa;
    --border: #d2d2d7;
    --radius: 18px;
    --radius-sm: 12px;
    --shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    --shadow-lg: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Display', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); line-height: 1.6;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }
  .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 24px 80px; }

  .header { text-align: center; padding: 60px 0 48px; }
  .header .badge {
    display: inline-block; background: var(--blue-light); color: var(--blue);
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 100px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .header h1 { font-size: 40px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.5px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .header .ver { font-size: 13px; color: var(--orange); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .header p { font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .section { margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .section-title {
    font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    margin-bottom: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  }
  .section-title .num {
    width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ===== Core Principle Banner ===== */
  .principle-banner {
    background: #1d1d1f; color: #fff; border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 32px 36px; margin-bottom: 32px; display: flex; gap: 28px; align-items: center;
  }
  .principle-banner .big-icon { font-size: 48px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .principle-banner h3 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; letter-spacing: -0.2px; }
  .principle-banner p { font-size: 14px; color: #a1a1a6; line-height: 1.6; }

  /* ===== Phase + Gate paired layout ===== */
  .phase-block { margin-bottom: 24px; }

  .phase-row {
    display: flex; align-items: stretch; gap: 0;
    border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }
  .phase-bar { width: 6px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .phase-body {
    flex: 1; background: var(--card); padding: 24px 28px;
    display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .phase-num {
    width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .phase-content { flex: 1; }
  .phase-content h3 { font-size: 19px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; letter-spacing: -0.2px; }
  .phase-content .sub { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .phase-content .detail { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.7; }

  /* Gate */
  .gate-connector {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; padding: 8px 0 8px 28px;
  }
  .gate-line { flex: 1; height: 2px; background: var(--border); border-radius: 1px; }
  .gate-badge {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: #fff; border: 2px solid var(--orange); border-radius: 100px;
    padding: 8px 18px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--orange);
    white-space: nowrap; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .gate-badge .gate-icon { font-size: 16px; }
  .gate-badge.pass { border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); }
  .gate-badge.fail { border-color: var(--red); color: var(--red); }

  /* Dual track */
  .dual-track { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .track-card {
    background: var(--card); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 24px 28px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow); position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .track-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 4px; }
  .track-card.a::before { background: var(--blue); }
  .track-card.b::before { background: var(--red); }
  .track-card h4 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .track-card .role { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-secondary); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .track-card ul { list-style: none; font-size: 14px; }
  .track-card li { padding: 5px 0; padding-left: 18px; position: relative; }
  .track-card li::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 11px; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--border); }
  .track-card.a li::before { background: var(--blue); }
  .track-card.b li::before { background: var(--red); }

  /* Claude + Codex model */
  .pairing-box {
    background: var(--card); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 28px 32px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow); margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .pairing-box h3 { font-size: 19px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .pairing-box .pair-desc { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .pairing-cols { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr; gap: 20px; align-items: start; }
  .pair-card {
    background: #f9f9fb; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); padding: 22px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .pair-card h4 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .pair-card .role-tag { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .pair-card ul { list-style: none; font-size: 13px; text-align: left; }
  .pair-card li { padding: 4px 0; padding-left: 16px; position: relative; }
  .pair-card li::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 10px; width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; }
  .pair-card.exec .role-tag { color: var(--blue); }
  .pair-card.exec li::before { background: var(--blue); }
  .pair-card.review .role-tag { color: var(--red); }
  .pair-card.review li::before { background: var(--red); }
  .pair-vs {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  .pairing-modes { margin-top: 20px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; }
  .mode-card {
    background: #f9f9fb; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); padding: 18px 20px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--purple);
  }
  .mode-card h4 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .mode-card p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary); }

  /* Sub tasks grid */
  .sub-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 14px; }
  .sub-card {
    background: var(--card); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); padding: 20px 22px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow); border-left: 4px solid var(--purple); font-size: 14px;
  }
  .sub-card h4 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .sub-card p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* Four questions */
  .four-qs { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 14px; }
  .q-card {
    background: var(--card); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); padding: 22px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow); text-align: center;
  }
  .q-card .q-num { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--blue); opacity: 0.15; margin-bottom: -8px; }
  .q-card h4 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .q-card p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* Format box */
  .format-box {
    background: #f9f9fb; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); padding: 22px 26px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 14px;
  }
  .format-box h4 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--text-secondary); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
  .format-box ol { padding-left: 18px; }
  .format-box li { padding: 3px 0; }

  /* Decision tree */
  .decision-tree { background: var(--card); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 32px; box-shadow: var(--shadow); }
  .dt-node { padding: 10px 0; }
  .dt-question {
    display: inline-block; background: #f5f5f7; border-radius: 100px;
    padding: 8px 18px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .dt-branch { margin-left: 28px; padding: 8px 0; border-left: 2px solid var(--border); padding-left: 20px; }
  .dt-branch.yes { border-left-color: var(--green); }
  .dt-branch.no { border-left-color: var(--red); }
  .dt-label { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .dt-yes { color: var(--green); } .dt-no { color: var(--red); }
  .dt-result { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; }

  /* Rules */
  .rule-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; }
  .rule-card {
    background: var(--card); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); padding: 18px 22px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow); font-size: 14px;
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;
  }
  .rule-card .icon { font-size: 22px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
  .rule-card strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .rule-card span { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 13px; }

  /* Trigger list */
  .trigger-list { list-style: none; font-size: 14px; }
  .trigger-list li { padding: 8px 0; padding-left: 22px; position: relative; }
  .trigger-list li::before { content: '●'; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 8px; font-size: 8px; color: var(--blue); }

  /* Anti-pattern callout */
  .callout {
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm); padding: 18px 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-size: 14px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;
  }
  .callout.warn { background: #fff3e0; border: 1px solid #ffe0b2; }
  .callout.info { background: var(--blue-light); border: 1px solid #cce0f8; }
  .callout .ca-icon { font-size: 20px; flex-shrink: 0; }

  .c1 { background: var(--blue); } .c2 { background: var(--red); }
  .c3 { background: var(--green); } .c4 { background: var(--purple); }
  .c5 { background: var(--orange); }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .dual-track, .sub-grid, .four-qs, .rule-grid, .pairing-cols, .pairing-modes { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .phase-body { flex-direction: column; }
    .principle-banner { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">

<!-- Header -->
<div class="header">
  <div class="badge">OKKI 方案复盘 · 方法论沉淀</div>
  <div class="ver">v2 — 审查即闸门，不累积到最后</div>
  <h1>复杂项目执行流程</h1>
  <p>4 阶段 + 每阶段出口闸门 · 双轨探索 → 框架收敛 → 分支并行 → 汇总攻击</p>
</div>

<!-- ====== Core Principle ====== -->
<div class="principle-banner">
  <div class="big-icon">⊘</div>
  <div>
    <h3>核心原则：没有「最终审查」，只有「每阶段审查」</h3>
    <p>v1 把执行可行性审查放在 Phase 5，前期付出大量成本到最后才发现问题 → 推翻重来。<br>v2 修正：审查不是 Phase，是每个 Phase 的出口闸门。问题在哪发现就在哪解决。</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ====== Claude + Codex Pairing Model ====== -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="section-title"><span class="num c1">▸</span> 生成者 + 审查者 持续配对</div>

  <div class="pairing-box">
    <h3>借鉴 Claude + Codex 协作模式</h3>
    <div class="pair-desc">生成者和审查者配对运行，审查不等到最后。每个产出生成后立刻被攻击。</div>

    <div class="pairing-cols">
      <div class="pair-card exec">
        <h4>生成者</h4>
        <div class="role-tag">Executor</div>
        <ul>
          <li>产出方案 / 规则 / 代码</li>
          <li>负责创造和构建</li>
          <li>Convo A / Main / Sub</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="pair-vs">vs</div>
      <div class="pair-card review">
        <h4>审查者</h4>
        <div class="role-tag">Reviewer</div>
        <ul>
          <li>找漏洞 / 矛盾 / 盲区</li>
          <li>不带推理偏见地攻击</li>
          <li>Convo B / Agent / 四问闸门</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pairing-modes" style="margin-top:20px;">
      <div class="mode-card">
        <h4>模式 1：对话级审查</h4>
        <p>Convo B 攻击 Convo A（只传概括版产出，不给完整上下文）<br>适合：大框架，需要深度上下文</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mode-card">
        <h4>模式 2：Agent 级审查</h4>
        <p>Main 生成产出后立刻调 code-reviewer agent 攻击<br>适合：分支细节，轻量快速，无偏见</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ====== 4 Phases + Gates ====== -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="section-title"><span class="num c1">▸</span> 四阶段流程（每阶段出口 = 四问闸门）</div>

  <!-- Phase 1 -->
  <div class="phase-block">
    <div class="phase-row">
      <div class="phase-bar c1"></div>
      <div class="phase-body">
        <div class="phase-num c1">1</div>
        <div class="phase-content">
          <h3>双轨探索</h3>
          <div class="sub">左右互搏 · 需求完全暴露 · 同时跑不等待</div>
          <div class="dual-track" style="margin-top:12px;">
            <div class="track-card a">
              <div class="role">对话 A</div>
              <h4>需求深挖</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>理解原始需求与场景</li>
                <li>挖掘隐藏约束</li>
                <li>提出初步方案框架</li>
                <li>记录关键假设</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="track-card b">
              <div class="role">对话 B</div>
              <h4>攻击审查</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>只接收 A 的概括版产出</li>
                <li>不带偏见攻击</li>
                <li>找漏洞、矛盾、盲区</li>
                <li>输出确认清单</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="gate-connector">
      <div class="gate-line"></div>
      <div class="gate-badge"><span class="gate-icon">🚪</span> 闸门：合并 A+B 做四问初筛</div>
      <div class="gate-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="callout info" style="margin-top:4px;">
      <span class="ca-icon">💡</span>
      <div>A 和 B 同时跑，不等。B 不给 A 的完整上下文——目的是不让 B 被 A 的推理过程影响，保持独立攻击视角。</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Phase 2 -->
  <div class="phase-block">
    <div class="phase-row">
      <div class="phase-bar c3"></div>
      <div class="phase-body">
        <div class="phase-num c3">2</div>
        <div class="phase-content">
          <h3>框架收敛</h3>
          <div class="sub">Main Conversation · 合并 → 回应 → 审查 → 拆子任务</div>
          <div class="detail" style="margin-top:8px;">
            <p>读 A 的需求理解 + B 的攻击清单 → 合并为方案框架 V1</p>
            <p>对 B 提出的漏洞逐一回应（修了 / 标为已知缺口 / 需用户决策）</p>
            <p>框架 V2 出来后 → <strong>立即跑四问审查</strong></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="gate-connector">
      <div class="gate-line"></div>
      <div class="gate-badge"><span class="gate-icon">🚪</span> 闸门：框架 V2 四问过审 → 拆子任务</div>
      <div class="gate-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="callout warn" style="margin-top:4px;">
      <span class="ca-icon">⚠️</span>
      <div><strong>关键教训</strong>：框架阶段就做四问，不等到分支细节讨论完。框架阶段暴露执行问题成本最低。今天 OKKI 方案在子对话 3 才发现「脚本每天怎么跑」这个执行框架性问题，就是因为框架定稿时没做执行审查。</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Phase 3 -->
  <div class="phase-block">
    <div class="phase-row">
      <div class="phase-bar c4"></div>
      <div class="phase-body">
        <div class="phase-num c4">3</div>
        <div class="phase-content">
          <h3>分支并行</h3>
          <div class="sub">2-4 个子对话独立推进 · 每个 Sub 产出后自己做四问</div>
          <div class="sub-grid" style="margin-top:12px;">
            <div class="sub-card"><h4>Sub-1</h4><p>单一分支<br>brainstorming 深挖<br>产出 + 四问自查</p></div>
            <div class="sub-card"><h4>Sub-2</h4><p>单一分支<br>brainstorming 深挖<br>产出 + 四问自查</p></div>
            <div class="sub-card"><h4>Sub-3</h4><p>单一分支<br>brainstorming 深挖<br>产出 + 四问自查</p></div>
          </div>
          <div style="margin-top: 12px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary);">
            每个 Sub 产出：分支方案 + 开放问题 + 数据缺口。不可推翻框架约束。
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="gate-connector">
      <div class="gate-line"></div>
      <div class="gate-badge"><span class="gate-icon">🚪</span> 闸门：每个 Sub 四问自查通过 → 汇总到 Main</div>
      <div class="gate-line"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Phase 4 -->
  <div class="phase-block">
    <div class="phase-row">
      <div class="phase-bar c2"></div>
      <div class="phase-body">
        <div class="phase-num c2">4</div>
        <div class="phase-content">
          <h3>汇总攻击 + 完整四问</h3>
          <div class="sub">Main 第二次交叉审查 · 矛盾 / 缺口 / 重复 → 完整四问 → 定稿</div>
          <div class="detail" style="margin-top:8px;">
            <p>读所有 Sub 产出 → 逐对比对：</p>
            <p style="margin-left:16px;">矛盾（Sub-1 假设 X，Sub-3 假设非 X）</p>
            <p style="margin-left:16px;">缺口（框架要求的点无人覆盖）</p>
            <p style="margin-left:16px;">重复（两个 Sub 定义同一概念但不同）</p>
            <p style="margin-top:8px;">和用户逐一确认 → 修正 → 对完整方案跑最后一轮四问 → 可落地方案定稿</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="gate-connector">
      <div class="gate-line"></div>
      <div class="gate-badge pass"><span class="gate-icon">✓</span> 终点：完整四问全部通过 → 可落地方案</div>
      <div class="gate-line"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ====== Four Questions Detail ====== -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="section-title"><span class="num c5">▸</span> 闸门内容：执行可行性审查四问</div>
  <div class="four-qs">
    <div class="q-card">
      <div class="q-num">01</div>
      <h4>数据从哪来？</h4>
      <p>OKKI 字段？消息解析？人工输入？外部 API？</p>
    </div>
    <div class="q-card">
      <div class="q-num">02</div>
      <h4>谁来取？</h4>
      <p>脚本能做？必须 AI 读上下文？需要人手动？</p>
    </div>
    <div class="q-card">
      <div class="q-num">03</div>
      <h4>什么时候取？</h4>
      <p>一次性写死？每天重复？事件触发？</p>
    </div>
    <div class="q-card">
      <div class="q-num">04</div>
      <h4>取不到怎么办？</h4>
      <p>降级规则？默认值？标记缺口后续补？</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top:14px; font-size:13px; color: var(--text-secondary); text-align:center;">任何一条四问答不上来 → 不下稿，先标注为缺口或解决它。</div>
</div>

<!-- ====== Key Formats ====== -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="section-title"><span class="num c1">▸</span> 关键格式 & 规则</div>
  <div class="dual-track" style="margin-bottom:16px;">
    <div>
      <h4 style="font-size:15px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:12px;">子对话输入格式（Main 拟定）</h4>
      <div class="format-box">
        <ol>
          <li>该分支要解决的具体问题（一句话）</li>
          <li>已定稿的框架约束（不可推翻）</li>
          <li>产出要求（格式 / 精度 / 决策边界）</li>
          <li>已知的边界条件和限制</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h4 style="font-size:15px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:12px;">上下文传递格式（对话概括）</h4>
      <div class="format-box">
        <ol>
          <li>当前阶段结论（300字内）</li>
          <li>已确认的规则/决策清单</li>
          <li>待解决的开放问题清单</li>
          <li>关键假设列表（需验证）</li>
          <li>下一步要做的事</li>
        </ol>
        <div style="margin-top:8px; font-size:12px; color: var(--orange);">不传完整对话历史——目的是传状态，不复现推理。</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="rule-grid">
    <div class="rule-card">
      <span class="icon">🔒</span>
      <div><strong>子对话不可推翻框架约束</strong><span>遇到影响框架的问题 → 标记回报 Main，不自行修改</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="rule-card">
      <span class="icon">📐</span>
      <div><strong>分支之间必须独立</strong><span>不互相依赖。2-4 个够用，>5 个说明拆太碎</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="rule-card">
      <span class="icon">🔄</span>
      <div><strong>上下文爆了 → 存概括 → 开新对话</strong><span>不要硬撑，概括格式传递状态即可</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="rule-card">
      <span class="icon">⏱️</span>
      <div><strong>双轨审查并发运行</strong><span>对话级审查（Convo B）+ Agent 级审查（code-reviewer）可叠加使用</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ====== Decision Tree ====== -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="section-title"><span class="num c1">▸</span> 决策树</div>
  <div class="decision-tree">
    <div class="dt-node"><div class="dt-question">收到任务</div></div>
    <div class="dt-branch no">
      <div class="dt-label dt-no">第一步判断</div>
      <div class="dt-node"><div class="dt-question">涉及 ≥3 个独立模块？</div></div>
      <div class="dt-branch yes">
        <div class="dt-label dt-yes">yes</div>
        <div class="dt-result">→ 完整 4 Phase 流程（含双轨互搏）</div>
      </div>
      <div class="dt-branch no">
        <div class="dt-label dt-no">no</div>
        <div class="dt-node"><div class="dt-question">新架构？≥2 个未验证假设？</div></div>
        <div class="dt-branch yes">
          <div class="dt-label dt-yes">yes</div>
          <div class="dt-result">→ 完整 4 Phase 流程</div>
        </div>
        <div class="dt-branch no">
          <div class="dt-label dt-no">no</div>
          <div class="dt-node" style="margin-top:8px;">
            <div class="dt-question" style="background:#e8f8ed;">简单任务 · 直接做</div>
          </div>
          <div style="font-size:13px; color:var(--text-secondary); margin-top:4px;">单文件修改 / 明确指令 / 不涉及架构决策</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ====== Trigger ====== -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="section-title"><span class="num c1">▸</span> 完整流程触发条件（满足任一）</div>
  <ul class="trigger-list">
    <li>涉及 ≥3 个独立模块 / 系统</li>
    <li>需要设计新架构或重构现有架构</li>
    <li>方案有 ≥2 个核心假设未经验证</li>
    <li>用户明确说「先想清楚再做」</li>
  </ul>
</div>

</div>
</body>
